    <h2>ðŸŒ¾ Tips for Healthy Soil</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Rotate crops to maintain soil nutrients</li>
      <li>Use compost and organic fertilizers</li>
      <li>Test your soil pH regularly</li>
      <li>Mulch to retain moisture</li>
